1.title: Baby Shark

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Baby Shark, Mama Shark, Papa Shark, Grandma Shark, and Grandpa Shark are out for a family swim. Sing along with this single of the Super Simple Baby Shark song.

2.title: Five Little Ducks

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: One of our favorite kids songs. "Five little ducks went out one day, over the hill and far away..."

3.title: How Many Fingers?

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: How Many Fingers is a super simple kids song to practice counting with your fingers and toes. Sing along with the friendly monsters.

4.title: The Ice Cream Song

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: We love ice cream so much we made a song about it.

5.title: This Is The Way

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Start the day with this super fun kids song, This Is The Way. Wash your face, comb your hair, brush your teeth, get dressed, and go to school.

6.title: Five Little Speckled Frogs

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Five little speckled frogs, sat on a speckled log, eating some most delicious bugs. YUM YUM. One of our favorite classic kids songs, Five Little Speckled Frogs is a nursery rhyme loved by kids and families around the world.

7.title: Mr. Golden Sun

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: It's the Mr. Sun song from Super Simple Songs.

8.title: Peekaboo

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: Peek-a-boo. We see you. And we hope you'll sing the peek-a-boo song with us. Where is kitty cat hiding? Can you find her? Let's play peek-a-boo.

9.title: 10 Little Dinosaurs

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: 10 Little Dinosaurs. 10 Stegosauruses. 10 Triceratops. 10 Pterodactyls. 10 Brontosauruses. And 10 Tyrannosaurus Rex. Wow.

10.title: The Muffin Man

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: Do you know the muffin man? Sing along with one of our favorite kids songs. This super simple take on the classic children's song, The Muffin Man, also introduces the Ice Cream Man and the Fruit Stand Man.

11.title: Apples & Bananas

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: Apples and Bananas is a super fun kids song and is great for playing with English vowel sounds. Ballet dancing bananas, twirling apples, and lots of silly fun. Join our friendly monster friends and sing along.

12.title: Do You Like Pickle Pudding?

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: Pickle Pudding?. If you liked "Do You Like Broccoli Ice Cream?" and "Do You Like Spaghetti Yogurt?", you'll love this new silly kids song from Super Simple Songs. What funny food combos can you think of?

13.title: Little Robin Redbreast

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot: It's Little Robin Redbreast vs. Kitty Cat in this Super Simple version of this classic kids song. Be careful, Kitty Cat.

14.title: Yes I Can!

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: "Yes, I Can!" is a super simple animal song that introduces a bunch of fun animals, action verbs, and the phrases, "Can you___?" and "Yes, I can. / No I can't."

15.title: Hickory Dickory... Crash!

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

15.plot: "Hickory dickory dock. The mouse went up the clock. The clock struck one. The mouse went down. Hickory dickory dock..." You know the traditional version of this nursery rhyme, but in this Super Simple version we also introduce a snake, a squirrel, a cat, a monkey, and an elephant!

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

17.plot: Let's take a picture. Get your camera out, we're going for a nature walk and taking some fun photos. Say cheese.

18.title: Eeny Meeny Miny Moe

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

18.plot: Play the classic choosing game, Eeney Meeney Miney Moe with this group of friends. Who do you think will be "it"?

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )

19.plot: 1 little, 2 little, 3 little sailboats. 4 little, 5 little, 6 little sailboats. 7 little, 8 little, 9 little sailboats. 10 little boats - splash.

episode of.title: Baby Shark & More Kids Songs: Super Simple Songs (TV Series 2017– )
